scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: These files cover all subjects related to Georgetown--social, economic, cultural, recreational, political, and historical.

relatedmaterial.head: Related Materials
relatedmaterial.p: Also see the Artificial Collection for rare historical items that have been removed from the Vertical Files. Vertical files related to Washington, D.C., history outside of Georgetown are housed in Washingtoniana at the interim location at Van Ness.
